How to build:

    ./build

How to use:

    The image is a components image consisting out of a kernel, initrd
    and filesystem rootfs image. For creating a running system out of
    these components a remote boot (aka PXE) infrastructure must be
    present and the respective component files needs to be placed there.
    Some documentation exists to support users with this task:

    * https://osinside.github.io/kiwi/working_with_images/setup_network_bootserver.html
